{2}<br/>
Returns: 8<br/>
There are eight spanning trees that contain the edge (1, 2):<br/>
{(1, 2), (1, 3), (1, 4)}<br/>
{(1, 2), (1, 3), (2, 4)}<br/>
{(1, 2), (1, 3), (3, 4)}<br/>
