{(1, 2), (1, 4), (3, 4)}<br/>
{(1, 2), (2, 3), (3, 4)}<br/>
{(1, 2), (2, 4), (3, 4)}</p>

<p>3)<br/>
4<br/>
{1,2,1}<br/>
{2,3,3}<br/>
Returns: 0<br/>
The set E contains a cycle, and thus there is no spanning tree that contains all these edges.</p>

<p>4)<br/>
